<P><br>
As the Morning sunlight breaks on the day of the funeral, the amazons set themselfs ready for amazons of other tribes to come and mourn the loss of one of there queens. The Dancers get dressed and painted to do the ceremonal dance. The Amazons finish the alter for where the Queen will be burned. And the stage of the Queens ROC and her daughters will stand for the service.<br>
<P><br>
