<br>
Kala made her way to where all the other amazon were seated or standing,prepareing for the funeral services. She nods to those who had arrived,but remained silent for the time being. She turned to those who were going to be doing the dancing and motioned for them to begin with the dance and song of the dead. <br>
<br>
At her signal,the dancing and song began. The song wasslow, low,and full of sadness and would continue on until more arrived for the services.<br>
<br>
Kala then slipped her mask over her face,then turned and walked over to the funeral pyre just as Kyran had disappeared. She looks at the pale face of her life long friend,and tears swell up in her eyes and trail down her cheeks underneath the mask. "You will be missed my friend,my sister." She bowed her head in silence for a long moment,then turned and looked once more to those who were gathering.<br>
<br>
She swollows hard,and tried to keep a focused mind without having a break-down. "The ceromony will start shortly,while preparation are being finished." <p>|| Kala of Smyrna ||</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uprincesslynn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Princess Lynn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#8A2BE2>(1/26/02 12:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=131.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Visits the Funeral</span><hr size=1> Lynn rides into the tribe for the funeral. She sees her mother and heads to her. She never knew maytha at all well, but knew she met alot to her mother, so she came. She taps her mothers shoulder, &quot;hello mother&quot; she said. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ukatrinasaphros.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Katrina Saphros</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#8A2BE2>(1/26/02 12:42 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=131.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The Funeral Begins</span><hr size=1> As the amazons arrive, the Funeral begins to start. The Children of Maytha go up to the stage dressed in there amazon attire. As Queen Kala goes up to the stage to begin to the ceremony.<br>
