<br>
The dancing and singing go from the saddness to the spirit release song and dance.<br>
<br>
Kala speaks over the music. "Fellow Athelfi,tonight we mourn the loss of Maytha Artemis Diansus,who served our nation selflessly for the duration of her life. She will be remembered as a great amazon and queen and a loving friend and mother who faught and died bravely against the ill wills of evil." As she speaks she returns to the pyre and adds another stick of fire to the already burning flames. "Let these flames release Maythas spirit." She then turns and takes a few paces away from the burning pyre. She stops and lowers her head in silence,as every amazon whos present will also do except those who are dancing around the pyre and singing. <p>|| Kala of Smyrna ||</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ukalaofsmyrna.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kala of Smyrna</A> at: 1/26/02 1:22:14 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ucrystalthelioness.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Crystal the Lioness</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#8A2BE2>(1/26/02 1:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=131.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re:</span><hr size=1> The Lioness Crystal,who seems to always follow Kala around,showed up. She padded over to Kala,and sat down on the ground beside her,her head lowering also,feeling the sadness all around the area. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 298<br> <font color=#8A2BE2>(1/26/02 4:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFro