~She walked back to where she stood as a deer pranced over to the Goddess and hung its head.~ <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazondelerium.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon DeLerium</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon</span><br>  Posts: 229<br> <font color=#8A2BE2>(1/26/02 3:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=131.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Princess of Themiscrya</span><hr size=1> *~ DeL rode swiftly into the lands of Sarmatia as she ehard of the death of there Queen. She had met Maytha only a handfull of times, she had watched the amazon in the war and knew how seriously she took the amazon name. She was horrified at this young strong Queen's life was cut short by such evil. She dismounted her mare at the center of the village and walked to where the funeral pyre was. Once there, she noticed the amazons, nodding respectfully to them all, she walked to the fire to say her goobye's to the Amazon Queen, then placed an amazon symbol of peace upon her on a piece of parchment, that would make sure he rspirit found peace..she then turned adn walked to the gathered amazons, bowing respectfully to the Goddess Artemis.~* <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenvaria.showPublicProfile?language=EN>QueenVaria</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://hometown.aol.com/cristalc15/images/tjcontenderpremiere.bmp" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 204<br> <font color=#8A2BE2>(1/26/02 9:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=131.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   